<li><a href="http://www.facstaff.bucknell.edu/mastascu/eControlHTML/Freq/Freq5.html" class="external text" title="http://www.facstaff.bucknell.edu/mastascu/eControlHTML/Freq/Freq5.html" rel="nofollow">Explanation of Bode plots with movies and examples</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.swarthmore.edu/NatSci/echeeve1/Ref/LPSA/Bode/BodeHow.html" class="external text" title="http://www.swarthmore.edu/NatSci/echeeve1/Ref/LPSA/Bode/BodeHow.html" rel="nofollow">How to draw piecewise asymptotic Bode plots</a></li>
<li><a href="http://lims.mech.northwestern.edu/~lynch/courses/ME391/2003/bodesketching.pdf" class="external text" title="http://lims.mech.northwestern.edu/~lynch/courses/ME391/2003/bodesketching.pdf" rel="nofollow">Summarized drawing rules</a> (<a href="/wiki/PDF" title="PDF" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a>)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.uwm.edu/People/msw/BodePlot/" class="external text" title="http://www.uwm.edu/People/msw/BodePlot/" rel="nofollow">Bode plot applet</a> - Accepts transfer function coefficients as input, and calculates magnitude and phase response</li>
<li><a href="http://mickpc.pbwiki.com/index.php?wiki=BodePlot" class="external text" title="http://mickpc.pbwiki.com/index.php?wiki=BodePlot" rel="nofollow">Bode Plotting on the HP49</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.abc.chemistry.bsu.by/vi/fit.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.abc.chemistry.bsu.by/vi/fit.htm" rel="nofollow">Circuit analysis in electrochemistry</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.en-genius.net/includes/files/acqt_013105.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.en-genius.net/includes/files/acqt_013105.pdf" rel="nofollow">Tim Green: <i>Operational amplifier stability</i></a> Includes some Bode plot introduction</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bode.cg.yu" class="external text" title="http://www.bode.cg.yu" rel="nofollow">Bode Plotter</a> Drag and Drop Bode diagram plotting tool by grafical definition of poles and zeros on polar diagram.</li>
<li>Gnuplot code for generating Bode plot: <a href="/wiki/File:Bode_plot_template.pdf" title="File:Bode plot template.pdf">DIN-A4 printing template (pdf)</a></li>
</ul>


